            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 drugfree-features-item">
            <img src="{{ 'features-item4.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" class="drugfree-features-item-img">
            <p class="drugfree-features-item-text">
                Educating & empowering women for a happier, healthier life
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


